## What is the purpose of the change

Fix service name mapping data being override when two process are creating persistent node in zookeeper at the same time.
BTW, this PR will fix the issue of `NodeExists for /dubbo/metadata`.

Root cause:
```java
    protected void createPersistent(String path, String data) {
        byte[] dataBytes = data.getBytes(CHARSET);
        try {
            client.create().forPath(path, dataBytes);
        } catch (NodeExistsException e) {
            // --------- Data will being overrided here --------------
            try {
                client.setData().forPath(path, dataBytes);
            } catch (Exception e1) {
                throw new IllegalStateException(e.getMessage(), e1);
            }
        } catch (Exception e) {
            throw new IllegalStateException(e.getMessage(), e);
        }
    }
```

